  <brief_title>Effects of TT301 on Cytokine Levels Post Endotoxin Challenge</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 1 Double-blind, Randomized, Placebo-controlled Study Evaluating the Effects of a Single Intravenous Dose of TT301 on LPS-induced Changes in Blood Cytokine Levels in Healthy Male Volunteers</official_title>
  <sponsors>
